}}{{TIDTOC|switch}} ==Overview== "A/N: PCB-KUS5-PA4" and "P/N: KUS5 Rev. A" is silkscreened on the board of the unit populating this entry. :A date code of '''9943''' is etched onto the bottom of the board.
This is presumed to be the first revision of the EZXS55W - there is no version / revision information on the label. :The appearance / design is completely different to later iterations of the EZXS55W - all the Ethernet ports + LEDs are on the front of the unit, the power jack is on the back, and the case is a greyish-white.
